type="local"
addr="marcelofiore">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link></fr:contributor></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The unique <fr:link
href="jms-00KF.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00KF">function</fr:link> <fr:tex>!_A \colon  A \to   { \mathopen {} \left  [ 1 \right  ] \mathclose {}}</fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00M8.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-00M8">surjective</fr:link> if and only if <fr:tex>A  \not = \varnothing</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
toc="false"
numbered="true"
show-heading="true"
